{"tid":1795003,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"係旺角比人偷左電話 收到個咁既訊息","createTime":"2019-12-23T14:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T09:02:52.000Z","uid":42565,"like":98,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"68db742fea2ecd65bae3aa03786640ffc96b3f7d","tid":1795003,"uid":42565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ME4kSL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FME4kSL4.jpg&h=0c879d12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用左無痕入左去，原來得殘體字，仲要用呢個登入都得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtCiErm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtCiErm.jpg&h=bc120559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲好笑係想拎埋我安全問題答案，緊係比埋佢啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QuuMOkf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQuuMOkf.jpg&h=4e5719c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後，交左比佢地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvCnmFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvCnmFE.jpg&h=41b4538b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家小心<br />\n<br />\n求教學有咩方法可以拎返部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ebe9d4d9b578041205791ac9e955c581bd22fb","tid":1795003,"uid":27605,"like":24,"dislike":6,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"唔好答<br />\n<br />\n我早排係個大陸apps買課左金買點睇書<br />\n諗住睇完就退<br />\n退左幾日<br />\n無啦啦有個野彈出黎叫我入apple id &amp; pw<br />\n個樣好似平時apple果個<br />\n好彩見到係itools  我已經幾萬年無用過<br />\n唔答問題 cancel左就無再出 嚇撚到apps都del埋<br />\n我估係條仆街唔順氣比我退左錢想爆我ac<br />\n<br />\n大陸網要apple id 一定唔可以比<br />\n一比左連資料都無埋 成世比人渣住春袋<br />\n如果你有閃片 電話無左就算啦"},{"pid":"c6a6d50b45ddeb350dcf6518bd4543fa9e3a8183","tid":1795003,"uid":250511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"find my phone"},{"pid":"6815ac0954307b5a964f74f2be76522d716263b7","tid":1795003,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201